shared_text:
WG Elementary & ELC
March 20 at 12:14 PM ·

WG families....we made a run to the Food Bank of Iowa this morning and have organized our little food bank at the elementary. Starting Monday...the front entry of the elementary will be open from 11-6 for families that are in need. We have prepackaged the items in the picture below...all that we ask is that you take only what you need. There is also milk and fruit in the fridge. There are also random items for the taking sitting on the tables.
We will keep you all updated as the needs continue to grow.
We are all in this together!
#WGBuildingFutures
Mr. B
Also....a huge shout out of thanks to Lisa Anderson and Brittany Wilkening for taking the lead during this time of need, and to Nurse Alex and Tiffany for their year round support of the food program.
